      "author": "TheManuelML",
      "description": "### New features\r\n- **New tool:** `filter notes` — Returns a list of note paths within a specified date range.  \r\n  You can choose whether to filter by creation or modification date, set a note limit, and sort results by *asc* or *desc*.   TheManuelML/obsidian-agent@48fd26cf75ee2e0d721ac58ff0b837219514d20d\r\n- **Image retention option:** When reading notes containing images, you can now choose to keep the images so the model can process them. TheManuelML/obsidian-agent@d85d411a76d095645afc0cb0ecd8952dba95d83c & TheManuelML/obsidian-agent@22a067b3731cd7366793a57adfcb42151c4b206d\r\n### Bugs fixed\r\n- **create note:** The tool no longer generates random tags. TheManuelML/obsidian-agent@19c6eecedcc6241ef185aea38442f05a12fe2b31\r\n### Refactors\r\n- Reorganized `utils` into subfolders for better maintainability. TheManuelML/obsidian-agent@d39ebca32fac784826ef61dcedfe8028f5ecb8e8\r\n- Updated to the latest LangChain packages. TheManuelML/obsidian-agent@006f1c682dca51fdfc29a0ff81812c2998716ba9",
